description: Inspired songs and Hymns to celebrate the life of Reverend Billy Graham.  1918-2018.  "The human heart is the same the world over. Only Christ can meet the deepest needs of our world and our hearts. Christ alone can bring lasting peace—peace with God, peace among men and nations, and peace within our hearts. He transcends the political and social boundaries of our world."
name: Rev. Billy Graham - In Memorium
